quran[10]{c,v,t}:
  45,33,"boneeji ɗi ɓe paggitinoo ɗiin feñana ɓe, ko ɓe njalkitatnoo kon fiiltoo ɓe."
  45,34,"ɓe mbi'ana hannde min njejjita mon hono no njejjitirɗon pottal ñangu mon hannde ngu, ko yiite woni hoɗorde mon on ndañata walladiiɓe."
  45,35,"ɗuum noon ko sabu on njaggarii aayeeje Alla ɗe njalkito nguurndam aduna hoomti on,hannde ɓe njaltata e yiite ɓe nduttataaka aduna ɓe ngolla golle lobbe haa Alla weleeɓe."
  45,36,"Woodanii Alla jettooje nder kammuuji e leydi Jom binnde."
  45,37,"Na woodani mbo manngu ndeer kammuuji e leydi ko Kaŋko woni mbo gooto foolata ñeeñɗo."
  46,1,"Haa, miim."
  46,2,"Jippagol deftere nden, ko immorde ka Allah, pooluɗo, ñeeño on."
  46,3,"Min tagiraali kammuuji ɗin e leydi ndin e ko woni hakkunde majji, si wonaa e goonga e lajala happaangal [fii mum]. Yedduɓe ɓen ko ɗuurniiɓe e ko ɓe ndentiniraa kon."
  46,4,"Maaku: "On nji'ii ko ndewoton kon hara wonaa Allah, kollee Kam ko ɗi tagi e leydi ndiin? Kaa hara hiɗi mari geɗal e [tagoore] kammuuji ɗiin? Awa ngaddanee lam deftere jippinaande ado ndee ɗoo ma batte ganndal, si wonii ko on gooŋɗuɓe !"."
  46,5,"Ko hommbo ɓuri majjude, wa on dewoowo ko wanaa Allah, ko jaabotaako mo haa Ñande Darngal? Hara ɗin [deweteeɗi] ko welsindiiɗi e dewal majji."